{"article_id":"vGcfEFCH541JOsoW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The stakes of Bernie Sanders ' take-it-to-the-convention strategy are rapidly rising","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"as fresh polls underscore Hillary Clinton 's vulnerabilities","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and predict a tight race between her and Donald Trump in the fall .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"After months of talk about the potential of a contested Republican convention , Trump , the presumptive GOP nominee , is quickly consolidating his party 's support","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"-- something","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Clinton is unable to do with Sanders still in the race .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"With only a few major nominating contests left ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"including California and New Jersey on June 7 ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Sanders lacks a credible mathematical path","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to overhauling Clinton 's wide lead in pledged delegates .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"with polls","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"showing Clinton 's general election advantage over Trump","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"evaporating ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"a lingering fracture in the Democratic party could be perilous for its chances","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to keep the White House .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Still , Sanders is not heeding calls from some Democrats","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to get out of the race","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"-- or at least cool his rhetoric during the final weeks of the primary season .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Instead , he kept up his blistering criticism of Clinton over the weekend","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and deepened his feud with the party establishment ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"including endorsing the primary challenger to Democratic National Committee Chairwoman Debbie Wasserman Schultz .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"`` The last","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"I heard","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"is that we are a democratic country ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"and that elections are about vigorous debates over the issues .","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"Secretary Clinton and I disagree , ''","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"Sanders told Jake Tapper Sunday on CNN 's `` State of the Union . ''","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"`` What the Democratic leadership has got to understand is that not all of my supporters go to these fancy fundraising dinners .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"They 're working people","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"who are hurting now ,","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"who want real change in the economy . ''","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"He added :","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"`` I hope","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"the Democratic leadership understands","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"they have to open up the process ,","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"bring those people in . ''","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"Sanders acknowledged in the interview","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that he has a `` very , very uphill fight '' in his quest","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"to overtake Clinton ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"given that he has won 46 % of pledged delegates so far","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and she has won 54 % .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"But he rebuked Democratic superdelegates","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"-- party office holders and lawmakers","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"who can vote","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"however they choose at the convention --","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"for overwhelmingly coming out for Clinton early on in what he said","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"was an `` anointment '' by the establishment and big money interests .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Clinton 's failure","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"to finally put away the Sanders campaign","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"is grating on the former secretary of state .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"`` I will be the nominee for my party , ''","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Clinton told CNN 's Chris Cuomo in an interview last week .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"`` That is already done , in effect .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"There is no way","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"I wo n't be . ''","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"On Sunday , she said","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"there will be an `` obvious need of us","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to unify the party ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"once she becomes the presumptive nominee .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"`` I will certainly do my part ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"reaching out to Sen. Sanders ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"reaching out to his supporters , ''","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"she said on NBC 's `` Meet the Press . '' `` And I expect him to do his . ''","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"The internal conflict comes at a time","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"when polls show","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that Trump is getting a dividend","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"from closing out the Republican primary race ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"and setting up what could be a close election against Clinton in November .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"A CNN/ORC poll from the beginning of May found Clinton leading Trump by 13 points .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"But in more recent surveys , there is increasing evidence of a bump in polling","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"as Trump consolidates GOP support .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"A Fox News poll last week showed Trump leading Clinton 45 % to 42 % , findings","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that were within the survey 's margin of error .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Meanwhile , a New York Times/CBS News national survey","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"released Thursday","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"had Clinton up by six points .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Washington Post/ABC News poll Sunday found a statistical dead heat ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"with Trump leading Clinton 46 % to 44 % among registered voters , figures","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that represent an 11-point swing since March .","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"The former secretary of state leads by six points among all adults","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"-- down from an 18-point lead in March .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Quinnipiac University polls in swing states Ohio , Florida and Pennsylvania this month also had the rivals effectively neck-and-neck .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Polls this far out from a general election can not offer a reliable picture","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"of what will happen in November .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"But they can shape the political environment","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"in which the early stages of the race evolves","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"and ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"if they continue to show Trump gaining in strength ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"are likely to increase pressure on Sanders","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"to bring the Democratic Party together .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"But Sanders does not see such polls as an argument","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that he should get out of the race","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"or dial back attacks on Clinton .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"In fact , he sees them as proof","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that he would be a superior general election candidate to the former first lady","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"-- most polls show him leading Trump .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"In the NBC interview , Clinton suggested","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"Sanders simply has n't been subjected to the rough and tumble of politics the way","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"she has .","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"It 's `` fair to say that I have been vetted and tested ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"and I think","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"that that puts me in a very strong position , ''","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"she said .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Referring to Sanders ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"she said ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"`` let me say","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"that I do n't think","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"he 's had a single negative ad ever run against him . ''","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"Sanders disputed the notion","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"that he is only doing better than Clinton","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"because he has not had to endure the years of partisan warfare","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"that have shredded her approval ratings . `` Any objective assessment of our campaign versus Clinton 's campaign ,","depth":16},{"id":114,"text":"I think ,","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"will conclude","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"we have the energy ,","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"we have the excitement ,","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"we have the young people ,","depth":18},{"id":119,"text":"we have the working people ,","depth":18},{"id":120,"text":"we can drive a large voter turnout ,","depth":17},{"id":121,"text":"so that we not only win the White House ,","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"but we retain ,","depth":18},{"id":123,"text":"regain control of the Senate ,","depth":18},{"id":124,"text":"do well in the House and in governor 's chairs up and down the line , ''","depth":17},{"id":125,"text":"Sanders told Tapper .","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"Latest polls clearly show","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that the lingering Democratic Party divisions are a challenge for Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"The Washington Post/ABC poll","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"released Sunday","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"showed","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"that in a match-up equation with Trump , Clinton currently gets 86 % of Democratic voters ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"meaning that a slice of the party coalition","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"that is not yet sold on her as nominee .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Making a decision","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"to leave a primary race","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"or to tone down attacks on a rival","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"who appears headed for victory","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"is the toughest choices","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"any candidate faces .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"It is a particularly acute dilemma for Sanders ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"given that he has won millions of votes ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"ignited a populist uprising in the Democratic Party","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"that no one saw coming","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"and is basking in an unprecedented reception to his democratic socialist ideas","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"that left him in the political wilderness for years in the Senate .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"He and his campaign team have dismissed the idea","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"that he could wreak lasting damage on Clinton","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"if she becomes the nominee ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"he will do whatever","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"it takes","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"to ensure","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"that Trump does not win the presidency .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"if his arguments about the process of the Democratic primary race leave the impression","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"that he has been unfairly treated","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"and that Clinton is somehow not the legitimate nominee ,","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"the task","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"of uniting the party","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"becomes far more difficult .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"That 's where Sanders ' clash with Wasserman Schultz is particularly concerning to some Democrats .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"The Vermont senator 's campaign has consistently accused the DNC chairwoman of tilting the race in favor of Clinton","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"and criticized the scheduling of debates on Saturday nights","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"when television audiences are lower ,","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"and the closed primaries","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"that bar independents in big states like New York .","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"Sanders is now backing Wasserman Schultz 's primary opponent in her Florida district , Tim Canova ,","depth":14},{"id":168,"text":"and left no doubt about the strengths of his feelings about her on Sunday .","depth":14},{"id":169,"text":"`` Well , clearly , I favor her opponent , ''","depth":16},{"id":170,"text":"Sanders told Tapper .","depth":16},{"id":171,"text":"`` His views are much closer to mine than as to Wasserman Schultz 's . ''","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"`` In all due respect to the current chairperson .","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"If","depth":16},{"id":174,"text":"( I was )","depth":18},{"id":175,"text":"elected president ,","depth":18},{"id":176,"text":"she would not be reappointed to be chair of the DNC . ''","depth":17},{"id":177,"text":"Sanders campaign manager Jeff Weaver also sent out a fundraising email to supporters Sunday","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"seeking contributions for Canova .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"For all the sudden handwringing in Democratic circles ,","depth":4},{"id":180,"text":"it 's still likely that Clinton will enjoy her own boost in the polls","depth":6},{"id":181,"text":"once she finally becomes the presumptive Democratic nominee","depth":6},{"id":182,"text":"similar to the one","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"Trump is enjoying now .","depth":6},{"id":184,"text":"For now , veteran Democrats appear to be ready to give Sanders some room .","depth":5},{"id":185,"text":"But the clock is ticking .","depth":5},{"id":186,"text":"`` After ( Clinton ) has actually won ,","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"after she actually has enough delegates","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"to win the nomination ,","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"Bernie needs to think about his legacy , ''","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"said Mark Alderman , a top Democratic Party donor","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"who was part of President Barack Obama 's transition team .","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"`` Bernie is in the middle of the tsunami --","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"he does n't have any perspective yet .","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"It will take a little time .","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"Unfortunately , he only has a little time .","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"He has got to get it together by July . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":395,"left":0,"right":394,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":394,"left":375,"right":393,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":375,"left":261,"right":374,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":245,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":203,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":200,"right":202,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":1,"right":199,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":4,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":212,"right":243,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":212,"left":206,"right":211,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":204,"right":205,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":11,"right":210,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":210,"left":208,"right":209,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":208,"left":207,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"p